\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"41.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 42,","    \"wort\": \"Belastbarkeit\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Flexibilität, Belastbarkeit und Mobilität werden in vielen Branchen von den Mitarbeitern verlangt.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"42.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 43,","    \"wort\": \"anonym\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Viele haben keine Lust mehr auf anonyme Hotelzimmer oder Apartments.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"43.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 44,","    \"wort\": \"kündbar\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Die Zimmer in der WG sind leichter und schneller kündbar.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"44.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 45,","    \"wort\": \"Netzwerk\",","    \"grammatik\": \"das Netzwerk\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Hier kann man private und berufliche Netzwerke knüpfen.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"45.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 46,","    \"wort\": \"Experiment\",","    \"grammatik\": \"das Experiment\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Er lebt dieses soziale Experiment bereits mehrere Jahre mit grossem Erfolg.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"46.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 47,","    \"wort\": \"Luxus\",","    \"grammatik\": \"der Luxus\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Eine Wohngemeinschaft bietet den Luxus, überall mitentscheiden und mitgestalten zu können.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"47.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 48,","    \"wort\": \"sich teilen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"teilt sich, teilte sich, hat sich geteilt\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Gemeinsam teilt man sich die Kosten für Einkäufe und die Unterstützung durch professionelle Kräfte\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"48.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {",