ort melden, sobald man etwas sagen möchte.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"69.opus\",","    \"teil\": 1","  },","  {","    \"id\": 70,","    \"wort\": \"zu Wort kommen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"kommt zu Wort, kam zu Wort, ist zu Wort gekommen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Während der lebhaften Diskussion musste er sich lautstark bemerkbar machen, um zu Wort zu kommen.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"70.opus\",","    \"teil\": 1","  },","  {","    \"id\": 71,","    \"wort\": \"beim Wort nehmen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"nimmt beim Wort, nahm beim Wort, hat beim Wort genommen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Er hat die Politikerin beim Wort genommen und die sofortige Umsetzung der Reform gefordert.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"71.opus\",","    \"teil\": 1","  },","  {","    \"id\": 72,","    \"wort\": \"umfassen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"umfasst, umfasste, hat umfasst\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Eine Abhandlung soll mindestens 350 Wörter umfassen.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"72.opus\",","    \"teil\": 1","  },","  {","    \"id\": 73,","    \"wort\": \"laut\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Genitiv oder Dativ  /Redewiedergabe: Präposition\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Laut unseres Schreibens / Laut unserem Schreiben können wir Ihnen zum jetzigen Zeitpunkt keine Zusage erteilen.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"73.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 74,","    \"wort\": \"nach\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Redewiedergabe: Präposition\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Meines Bruders Meinung nach sollte Vater keine anstrengende Reise mehr unternehmen.\",","    \"lektion\": 1,","    \"audio\": \"74.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 75,","    \"wort\": \"zufolge\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Redewiedergabe: Präposition\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Dem Autor zufolge könnte ein Handyverbot in Schulen sinnvoll sein.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"75.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 76,","    \"wort\": \"wie\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Redewiedergabe: Nebensatz\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wie es im Text heisst, sollte man Krieg durch politische Verhandlungen verhindern.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"76.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 77,","    \"wort\": \"wie\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Redewiedergabe: Nebensatz\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wie mein Kollege berichtete, war die Gefahr durchaus voraussehbar / vorhersehbar.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"77.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 78,","    \"wort\": \"Konjunktiv I Vergangenheit\",","    \"grammatik\": \"indirekte Rede\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Er behauptete, er sei nicht im Bild gewesen.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"78.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 79,","    \"wort\": \"Infinitvsatz\\nVergangenheit\",","    \"grammatik\": \"indirekte Rede\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Der Verdächtige behauptete, gestern den ganzen Abend zu Hause gewesen zu sein.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"79.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 80,","    \"wort\": \"Konjunktiv II\",","    \"grammatik\": \"indirekte Rede, nur, wenn nötig\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wir meinen, wir könnten diese Aufgaben\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"80.opus\",","    \"teil\": 2","  },","  {","    \"id\": 81,","    \"wort\": \"Vereinbarkeit\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Ohne mobiles Büro wäre für mich die Vereinbarkeit von Beruf und Familie gar nicht möglich.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"81.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 82,","    \"wort\": \"Daten\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die (Pl.)\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Es ist sehr hilfreich, ständig Zugriff zu seinen eigenen Daten zu haben.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"82.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 83,","    \"wort\": \"sich treffen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"mit\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Man kann Projekte bearbeiten, ohne sich allzu oft mit den Mitarbeitern zu treffen.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"83.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 84,","    \"wort\": \"Erreichbarkeit\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Man sollte Zeiten für die eigene Erreichbarkeit definieren.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"84.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 85,","    \"wort\": \"ständig\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Man sollte sich nicht verpflichtet fühlen, ständig erreichbar zu sein.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"85.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 86,","    \"wort\": \"ausschalten\",","    \"grammatik\": \"schaltet aus, schaltete aus, hat ausgeschaltet\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Bei Besuch schalten wir das Handy aus.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"86.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 87,","    \"wort\": \"voll und ganz\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wenn ich immer für alle erreichbar bin, bin ich in Wahrheit nie voll und ganz für jemanden da.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"87.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 88,","    \"wort\": \"verarbeiten\",","    \"grammatik\": \"verarbeitet, verarbeitete, hat verarbeitet\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wenn man zu viele Informationen erhält, kann man sie kaum noch verarbeiten.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"88.opus\",","    \"teil\": 3","  },","  {","    \"id\": 89,","    \"wort\": \"Opfer\",","    \"grammatik\": \"das\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wer nicht Contra bieten kann, wird leicht zum Opfer von Hohn und Spott.\",","    \"lektion\": 2,","    \"audio\": \"89.opus\",","    \"teil\": 4","  },","  {","    \"id\": 90,","    \"wort\": \"sprachlos\",","    \"grammatik\": \"gegenüber + Dativ\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wem keine schnelle Antwort einfällt, der bleibt sprachlos gegenüber Frechheiten.\",","    \"