er nicht auf den zu zahlenden Wein aufmerksam macht.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"220.opus\",","    \"teil\": 4","  },","  {","    \"id\": 221,","    \"wort\": \"Instanz\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die, Instanzen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Eine spezielle Instanz im menschlichen Bewusstsein sagt dem Menschen, wie er sein eigenes Handeln beurteilen soll.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"221.opus\",","    \"teil\": 4","  },","  {","    \"id\": 222,","    \"wort\": \"Gewissen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"das\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Das Gewissen wird von Gefühlen, Willen und Vernunft gesteuert.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"222.opus\",","    \"teil\": 4","  },","  {","    \"id\": 223,","    \"wort\": \"Stimme\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Das Gewissen ist eine innere Stimme, die unser Handeln bestimmt.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"223.opus\",","    \"teil\": 4","  },","  {","    \"id\": 224,","    \"wort\": \"Grundlage\",","    \"grammatik\": \"für + Akkusativ, die, Grundlagen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Das Gewissen ist die Grundlage für verantwortungsbewusstes Handeln.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"224.opus\",","    \"teil\": 4","  },","  {","    \"id\": 225,","    \"wort\": \"wegen/weil, da\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Nominalisierung und Verbalisierung von Kausalsätzen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"wegen der starken Konkurrenz/weil die Konkurrenz stark ist\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"225.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 226,","    \"wort\": \"durch/indem\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Nominalisierung und Verbalisierung von Modalsätzen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"durch die Verlegung der Produktion ins Ausland/indem sie die Produktion ins Ausland verlegen\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"226.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 227,","    \"wort\": \"durch/dadurch, dass\",","    \"grammatik\": \"Nominalisierung und Verbalisierung von Modalsätzen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"durch das grenzenlose Einkaufen im Internet/dadurch, dass man im Internet grenzenlos einkaufen kann.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"227.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 228,","    \"wort\": \"Druck\",","    \"grammatik\": \"der\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Durch die Globalisierung steigt der Wettbewerbsdruck enorm.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"228.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 229,","    \"wort\": \"verlegen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"verlegt, verlegte, hat verlegt\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Die Produktion wird ins Ausland verlegt, wo das Unternehmen von billigeren Arbeitskräften profitiert.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"229.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 230,","    \"wort\": \"Rohstoff\",","    \"grammatik\": \"der, Rohstoffe\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Rohstoffe können weltweit zu den günstigsten Preisen gekauft werden.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"230.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 231,","    \"wort\": \"Schattenseite\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Die Globalisierung hat jedoch auch Schattenseiten.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"231.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 232,","    \"wort\": \"gering\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"In den Industrieländern verlieren Menschen mit geringen Qualifikationen ihre bisherige Arbeit.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"232.opus\",","    \"teil\": 5","  },","  {","    \"id\": 233,","    \"wort\": \"Kredit\",","    \"grammatik\": \"der, Kredite\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Sie haben eine tolle Geschäftsidee, wollen aber keinen Kredit bei einer Bank aufnehmen.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"233.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 234,","    \"wort\": \"Fremdfinanzierung\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Crowdfunding ist eine alternative Fremdfinan-zierung.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"234.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 235,","    \"wort\": \"erreichen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"erreicht, erreichte, hat erreicht\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Wird diese Summe nicht in der vorgegebenen Zeitspanne erreicht, erhalten die Kapitalgeber ihr Geld zurück.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"235.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 236,","    \"wort\": \"begrenzen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"begrenzt, begrenzte, hat begrenzt\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Die Crowdfunding-Aktion muss zeitlich begrenzt werden.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"236.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 237,","    \"wort\": \"ausgeben\",","    \"grammatik\": \"gibt aus, gab aus, hat ausgegeben\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Die Gelder müssen zweckgebunden ausgegeben werden.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"237.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 238,","    \"wort\": \"präzis\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Bei einem Bankgespräch sollten Sie Ihr Produkt möglichst präzis beschreiben.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"238.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 239,","    \"wort\": \"eingehen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"auf + Akkusativ, geht ein, ging ein, ist eingegangen\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Gehen Sie auf die Bedenken des Kreditgebers ein.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"239.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 240,","    \"wort\": \"gelassen\",","    \"grammatik\": \"\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Auch wenn man Ihnen unangenehme Fragen stellt, sollten Sie gelassen bleiben.\",","    \"lektion\": 4,","    \"audio\": \"240.opus\",","    \"teil\": 6","  },","  {","    \"id\": 241,","    \"wort\": \"Terminvereinbarung\",","    \"grammatik\": \"die\",","    \"beispiel\": \"Um die Ablehnung einer Terminvereinbarung zu verhindern, sollte man sich gut vorbereiten.\",","    \"lekti